          "description": "I have been to so many vets over the 14 years I\u2019ve had my Boxer dog Nala. Every vet tries to fatten the bill and add so much unnecessary stuff just to get money out of me, but Dr. Suchanek is the opposite of that. I\u2019ve been seeing him for about 5 years or so, and with each visit my trust and faith grew in him. He was the Doctor who found my dogs mass which turned out to be cancer. He was able to give me the best medical advice on how to move forward, and was a huge help during my dogs last few days. The animal world, and pet owners are super lucky  to have Dr Suchanek as a Vet. I recommend everyone and anyone to see Dr. Suchanek and his team. If I ever get another dog, this is the only vet I will use.",
